    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🔁 Automated Follow-Up Manager\n\n**Purpose**\nKeeps following up with leads who received an email but never replied. AI generates a fresh follow-up message each time based on whether the lead opened the previous email or not.\n\n**How it works**\nRuns every **6 hours** → finds leads with no reply → AI generates a context-aware follow-up → checks unsubscribe list → sends via Gmail → updates follow-up count.\n\n**Follow-up Sequence**\n- Day 3 → Value-add email (new insight or resource)\n- Day 7 → Gentle nudge (simple yes/no question)\n- Day 14 → Breakup email (last attempt)\n- After 4 follow-ups → Lead moves to **nurture list**",
        "height": 576,
        "width": 272
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        160,
        -608
      ],
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "id": "ab963f29-7c98-48e2-a68d-678ee294bd5e",
      "name": "Sticky Note"
